r the house. He would never - a man to travel about and go out back and forth. Bit of gardening, and - we'd all do a bit of gardening in our turns. But - he never got - he'd never go out. Only to chapel.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Do you remember any outings with your parents?
