\insrsid5572000\charrsid13850017 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 cupful in the bottom, and he'd say here you are West, drink it up. And every pub he had a half p}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
