\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 You said you had one holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 One holiday, Weston for a week. And - the only thing you could do there see was go and sit on the
 sands or lay on the sands. With my two - my sister and her young man, and their friends. And I had been ill, that was it, that's why I went else I wouldn't have gone. But cor gosh you were -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Could you tell me how you spent Saturdays in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Home or -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 When you were still at school?
