\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Were you ever given lessons by one of your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 A tutor or a governess?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 No. No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 How old were you when you first went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Four year old.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 What time of the morning did you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Nine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Whe}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4881359\charrsid13850017 n}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 
 did you come back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 You went for the whole day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 What kind of school was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Elementary school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Boys only or mixed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Boy - mixed, mixed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 How did you get to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Ah, walked a mile and a half.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 How long did it take you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Oh, about twenty minutes, half an hour.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Who went with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Oh, a crowd of the boys from the village like.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Where did you have your midday meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Sometimes walk home, sometimes take sandwiches with us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 You wouldn't have very much time would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Yes. Mm. We used to walk home, and see - we'd come out of school - at twelve o'clock}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4881359\charrsid13850017 . We\rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 
d run all the way from Tapswells, to the Tong, and we'd do it in about twenty minutes. We'd have our dinner, and we'd start back about twenty - ten past one, and we'd run back to Tapswell. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 When you didn't have your dinner at home what would you eat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Oh, bread and butter and cheese or bread and butter and jam. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 What did you think of school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Not very much. But - I was very for
tunate, I had a wonderful teacher and the funny - I'll give you a little story now. She was one of the finest teachers in the world. And a beautiful looking woman she was. And - Miss Davis. And I was very smart on mental arithmetic. And she would have a -
 a ring in the class, and she'd say now - the answer to this, and she'd be putting numbers down on the board and I'd say, ninty}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4881359\charrsid13850017  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 four m'm. Now that - Howell, stop it, don't answer any more, come to the top of the class. I'd go to the top and then I'd stop th
ere. So of course - and she'd make me sit up. I remember one time the paper burnt - in the grate, and she were an attractive woman, and the paper - the - burnt paper flew up and went in to her hair. And she said, come here Howell, get this paper out of my
 
hair. And she were kneeling down and - and all those boys you know - watching me and I - I felt awfully embarrassed. But anyhow, I was a big favourite of hers, her name was Edith Davis. You listen to what I'm going to tell you now. So - I left school, she
 
married - a Mr Perret, he had a - he was schoolmaster in Cardiff, Splott, and - after they were married and went away I hadn't seen her for donkeys years. Well one day - a lady came here to live next door. So - I'm the warden here of course, so she came t
o
 see the place and she said - oh I think it's a lovely place here don't you? And I thought - what a superior looking woman. What a lovely woman. I said, yes, it's a lovely place. And she said, I - I said - where are you now at the moment? OH well, she sai
d
, I - I - at the moment I'm in an hostel, I've just come back from Tangiers, I've been there sixteen years. Oh, I said, have you? Yes, she said, a missionary work. Oh I said, you're from this part? Yes, she said, I taught in - Caerphilly grammar school fo
r
 years. Good gracious, yes, I'm teaching - French - French mistress. Oh, I said. Of course I'm from Tapswell. I said, what name did you say? Edith Per - Mrs Perret she said. I said, you're not Edith Perret's daughter? She said, I am, why? God, I said, Edi
th Davis. I said, you - that were my schoolteacher, her daughter's living here now. Sixty years of age. Aye. And she's an angel from heaven this one. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Did you like school or did you dislike it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Oh, no, I - I - I liked school but I - I - I - I wasn't keen on carrying on school work mind.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 How did you feel about the teachers, was it only Miss Davis taught you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Oh no, no, I - oh, there were some bad teachers there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 What did you feel about them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 I doubt some of them - in thos
e days - should have been in a - on a farm. They were too ignorant to be teachers. Oh - and brutes. Brutes. We had one teacher there, he had a big nose, they used to call him sloper nose. And - he'd have a cane by him from - the moment he got in school 't
i
l the moment he got out. And you only want to - you only had to - turn your eyes the wrong way and he'd slash you across the bac, right across the neck with the cane. Yes. I never had no - no place for some of the teachers. And there was others, beautiful
 
mind. The headmaster in - the school in Tapswell were Mr - Edmonds, and they opened a little school in Tongwynlais, infants school, and his wife - became the mistress there. And me living close by there. So - I got now well away now. One dinner time - he 
said, Griffiths, come here a minute. So he said, you're living close - he said, you're living close by - the infants school aren't you? I said, yes sir. Take this down to my wife will you? Give me three}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4881359\charrsid13850017  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 pence now, take this - it was her dinner see. Come dow
n, and when I got to the school - oh you live by here Howell? Yes. Oh, right, thank you very much. I'll see you tomorrow. So this was a permanent job. See? So - and - I was a wicked bugger mind, so - one day - I wanted to go in to the circus, there was a 
circus come, and I didn't have any money. So he give me three}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4881359\charrsid13850017  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 
pence to come down. And it was sixpence to go in the circus. So I brought the thing to this woman and she used to - every day she used to say, did Mr - Edmonds give you anything? I'd say, yes tha
nk you m'm. So this morning she said, - I said, no he didn't. So she give me three}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4881359\charrsid13850017  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 
pence. Oh - the following day I went - went up there and old Edmonds looked at me, he give me the three}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4881359\charrsid13850017  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 
pence, and he said, when you go today mind there's no circus then, tell her you've had it. Tell her you've had it. Oh.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Did the teachers emphasise certain things as important in life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Oh aye, aye, aye. But the important in their - as far as they were concerned the impor}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4881359\charrsid13850017 t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 ance in life was - to learn. Learn. Without learning you'll be nowhere.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 What about manners?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Oh mind - manners were good and all that, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 And tidiness?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Oh and tidiness, aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Punctuality?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Yes. Oh you wouldn't be late going to school and I mean - you'd have to go 
tidy, well your parent - my parents wouldn't allow us to go untidy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Ways of speaking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Aye, always spoke properly and - there were no slang if you understand me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 If you did something the teachers disapproved of what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Oh damn, have the cane. Yes, oh -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 How did they punish the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Caning. Caning and - and - brutal some of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Girls as well as boys?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Yes. Some of them brutal. They'd hit you, give you as much as eight and ten cuts on - three or four 
on each hand, and then across the back and across the legs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 For what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 
