er now, the cashier Edwardes, oh gentlemen he said - sit down and make yourself comfortable. Mr Morgan is - is busy for a while. On comes two bottles of whisky girl. Box of biscuits. And you're there, talking about. Oh, he said, well how long before Mr Ed
