Oh gosh, I had a - I had a class in Sunday school for years. Yes. I - always went to chapel and - always went in the nights. And - today you know - I don't go very often today, I went last - but - I baby}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14955578\charrsid13850017 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 sit for my - son and his wife, he's the organist in the chapel you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Did you take an interest in politics?
