\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Oh friends I already had. Kept the same -
