here. And they were in Bridgend on holiday, and we went to dance in Bridgend, and borrowed this - pony and trap, from a milkman in Tapswell, Thomas. Up over Lantwisant Common and - gets to Bridgend, put the horse and cart up - in a pub called the Welcome 
