- the job that I had to be - had to be done was started. And then I might go back home and - do a bit of work in the house for the - because the wife were delicate see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Would you go back in time for the children}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14955578\charrsid13850017 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
