hello, what's the matter? What are you doing here he said. Well I said, because you hadn't come home, what's the matter? And then he told me all about it and the - the girl had a baby going down in the car. So I said, all right, you go back home now. Aye.
 
So he went back home, and I waited there for to take the mother back home. Aye, the next boy. He was courting a young girl in - in Whitchurch here. And - he said he'd got afternoon off. Could I have a lend of the car to go - take Vera out? I said, where? 
