nly to Row Park, he said. I said, yes, and no farther mind. And - I'm going to Cobridge to work - the afternoon, and coming back form Cobridge - and as I'm across - past the Cobridge Common - here he is going across the Common with his girlfriend. I didn'
t
 say a word, I just kept going. But I wasn't in the house four minutes - before he was there. See he walked in the house and brought his girl in with him. So he said, where have you been working dad? I said, Cobridge. I said, where have you been? Oh, he s
