\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Did you want them to share their worries with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Oh yes, if they had any worries at all I wanted to know at once.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 How did you want them to behave towards you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7606694 HG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 
I expected them to treat me properly. But this is again - this is again you see, I never had any difficulty in that. I - I - I was more of a - a - more of a boy wi
th 'em. See well because when they were - even when they were twenty - I used to go and put the gloves on with 'em up in our spare room. Yes, and box with them and - oh yes, I mean - I may have been fortunate and my be different to other people, but I was
 very fortunate with my children. And the funny thing they are grown up today, they're - I've got one fifty-five, fifty-six. And they're always the - they're the same today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14495273 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8662948\charrsid13850017 Did you let them join in when grown ups were talking?
